  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Comparison of malignant and non-malignant disorders associated bone marrow hemophagocytosis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is a retrospective study comparing malignant and non-malignant disorders associated bone
      marrow hemophagocytosis. The medical record of patients who had documented evidences of
      hemophagocytosis in bone marrow are reviewed. The clinical and biological characteristics are
      compared according to the underlying disorders of hemophagocytosis.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
